   Interact; AAAS, Sci Robot},
Abstract = {Recent advances in generative AI have resulted in a rapid and dramatic
   increase to the fidelity of created artifacts, from realistic-looking
   images of faces {[}10] to antimicrobial peptide sequences that treat
   diseases {[}5] to faked videos of prominent business leaders {[}4, 11].
   We believe that people skilled within their creative domain can realize
   great benefits by incorporating generative models into their own work:
   as a source of inspiration, as a tool for manipulation, or as a creative
